{"tid":293777,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃雨冧露台：新居住唔慣　災民冀返劏房","createTime":"2017-06-22T12:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T15:48:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a94dee366d7344d9b5370b4ce5aefa43b2e78c3c","tid":293777,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"06月22日(四) 18:13<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170622/photo/bkn-20170622181303519-0622_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170622182509\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170622%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170622181303519-0622_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170622182509&h=780367a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下午3時半，住在涉事單位的陳先生、王女士及2名住客，一起返回紅磡機利士南路50號塌露台屋的單位收拾物品。住在同一層樓的王女士表示，她在10年前來港，任清潔工，有一名20歲、仍在求學的女兒，兩母女同住涉事單位，一人租用一間房，房租連水電分別需2000及2500港元，而廁所及廚房則共用。王憶述事發時聽到「嘭」一聲巨響，還以為「行雷」，直至警員上樓疏散，她探頭一望，始知陳的睡房底部塌陷，慌忙落樓疏散。<br />\n<br />\n王女士又指出，經政府部門人員轉介下，獲安排到附近的黃埔街一個1廳3房的單位暫住，暫不用交租，未知可以住到何時，惟該唐樓沒有升降機、又少人住，她整晚覺得「好高、好驚」，睡到凌晨3時就扎醒，坦言「住喺嗰度瞓得唔好」，希望能盡快返回原本的劏房居住，她在今年4月已申請公屋，希望能盡快上樓。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生表示，他有長期病患，希望收拾藥物及衣服離開，昨日被政府清理的家當，已被運到九龍灣存放，稍後會去認領。<br />\n<br />\n在下午約5時半，屋宇署將涉事的唐樓解封，交回業主管理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170622/bkn-20170622181303519-0622_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170622%2Fbkn-20170622181303519-0622_00822_001.html&d=bg4WwxFL4h8rV85dI2MhqsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=58522f6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170622/bkn-20170622181303519-0622_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ffea850938af1855814583e73f9b23e5b4c4ce88","tid":293777,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T12:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069b8e106b363bbd11192c94eea765a20ef91d77","tid":293777,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T12:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5532b002603918c7f88860fae9007b28115953ec","tid":293777,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"她整晚覺得「好高、好驚」<br />\n<br />\n驚乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd44f1f1381b1b2b6264864448bde575fbe68de1","tid":293777,"uid":48582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T12:35:34.000Z","msg":"黃埔街準備拆，佢想住都住唔耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca82ed60a1d8962b0a8b7d863df68142a4ae30bc","tid":293777,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T12:36:16.000Z","msg":"奴性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4194f7acde25cb69cc09c7710d2d948c4e7696","tid":293777,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奴性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想R公屋咋"},{"pid":"e6d7d74d65cce0cb7bec8f90f1e868e93592289f","tid":293777,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"黃埔一定好住啦"}]}